Package: vigiar
Type: Package
Title: VIGIAR Environmental Health Data for Rio de Janeiro
Version: 0.7.1.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Ryan",
           family = "Santos",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ryan.paulo@gsuite.iff.edu.br",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-6770-2001")))
Author: Ryan Santos
Maintainer: Ryan Santos <ryan.paulo@gsuite.iff.edu.br>
Description: Specialized package to download, process, validate and
    analyse environmental health surveillance data from Brazil's
    VIGIAR (Vigilancia em Saude Ambiental) public Power BI dashboard,
    maintained by the Brazilian Ministry of Health, with focus on the
    state of Rio de Janeiro. Includes the official registry of 92
    municipalities with health macro-regions (SES-RJ), automatic RJ
    filtering, IBGE code validation, PM2.5 air quality processing,
    benchmark and compliance auditing, structured logging, local caching,
    data snapshots with SHA256 checksums, schema version locking, and
    integration-ready municipality codes for SIH, SIM and DATASUS.
    Built on httr2, dplyr, cli, openssl, and tibble.
